@startuml
title B8 Slice 4 - Retrieval Cache + Incremental Reindex

actor "Board / Agent Event" as Event
rectangle "Issue Retrieval" as Retrieval
database "retrieval_cache_entries" as Cache
database "project_knowledge_revisions" as Revisions
database "knowledge_documents\nknowledge_chunks" as Knowledge
rectangle "Workspace Import" as Import

Event --> Retrieval : queryText
Retrieval --> Cache : query_embedding lookup
Cache --> Retrieval : hit / miss
Retrieval --> Retrieval : dense query embedding
Retrieval --> Knowledge : hybrid retrieval

Import --> Revisions : read last head/tree
Import --> Import : compare head/tree
Import --> Knowledge : incremental changed paths
Import --> Knowledge : deprecate removed paths
Import --> Revisions : bump revision

note right of Retrieval
Query embedding cache is safe because
it depends only on query text and model fingerprint.
end note

note right of Import
Tree unchanged -> skip
Changed paths only -> incremental
Deleted path -> deprecate existing documents
end note

@enduml
